You must specify a key file.

Usage: ntfsdecrypt [options] -k name.pfx device [file]

    -i, --inode num         Display this inode

    -k  --keyfile name.pfx  Use file name as the user's private key file.
    -e  --encrypt           Update an encrypted file
    -f  --force             Use less caution
    -h  --help              Print this help
    -q  --quiet             Less output
    -V  --version           Version information
    -v  --verbose           More output

